Gardener Hailuo and her family live in Changping District, Beijing, the capital of China. She loves taking photos of her plants and decorating her garden with pretty items, such as statues and colorful bowls. She recently took some pictures of her garden covered in snow. Check them out. (Photos are provided by Aluo.) For more: Backyard Landscape Explore one of the most beautiful private gardens in Beijing Explore a private 'grassland' floating in the air (If you want to contribute and have specific expertise, please contact us at nature@cgtn.com.)